# Avatar

The Avatar component displays user avatars, brand marks, or other circular content, supporting images, text (slot / name), and icons.

## Basic Usage

::TuffDemo{title="Avatar" description="Image, name, icon, and fallback content." code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center;">
      <TxAvatar src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1?v=4" />
      <TxAvatar name="Talex DreamSoul" />
      <TxAvatar icon="user" />
      <TxAvatar>U</TxAvatar>
    </div>
  </template>
---
#preview
<div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center;">
  <tx-avatar src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1?v=4" />
  <tx-avatar name="Talex DreamSoul" />
